Rhea Seehorn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rhea_Seehorn 0 Rhea Seehorn (; born May 12, 1972) is an American actress known for playing Kim Wexler in Better Call Saul. She is also known for prior roles in NBC's Whitney, ABC's I'm With Her and TNT's Franklin Bash.
